name: XmlNode
desc: Represents a node in an XML document tree (DOM-like structure).

desc: Returns the child element with the given name.

desc: Returns all child elements with the given name.

desc: Returns the value of an attribute by name.

name: getParent
desc: Returns the parent node of this node.

name: getText
desc: Returns the text content of this node.

desc: Returns the current token type (START_ELEMENT, END_ELEMENT, TEXT, etc.).

desc: Returns the current element name if at an element token.

name: getText
desc: Returns the text content of the current token.

name: nextToken
desc: Advances the parser to the next XML token.

desc: Represents a node in a YAML document tree (DOM-like structure).

desc: Returns all child nodes with the given key.

name: getElements
desc: Returns the list of all child nodes in a sequence.

name: getKeys

name: getNodeType
desc: Returns the type of this YAML node.

name: getText
desc: Returns the scalar value of this node.

name: toObject
desc: Converts this node to a Dart object of type T.

name: getAnchor

desc: Returns the current token type (mapping, sequence, scalar, etc.).

desc: Advances the parser to the next YAML token.
